setTitle

void setTitle(java.lang.String title)
Set the title of this DocumentLibrary. The title is used in the library URL, so only valid URL characters are allowed. Valid characters are a-z, A-Z, 0-9 and the special characters " $-_.+!*(),".

Parameters:
title - Title to be set
